						<div class="postbody">Disch: I wasn't planning on *reading* $4015 at all, just writing to it. Either way, that behavior was what I was afraid of. If 1-&gt;0-&gt;1 on 4015.4 restarts the DMC sample, then I probably shouldn't use it for silencing the channel DMC channel. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />
